title: "Awesome AI Gateway"
message: "If you use this list or its data, please cite it."
type: dataset
abstract: >-
  A curated, bilingual, vendor-neutral directory of 100+ AI gateways / LLM
  proxies, with a reproducible token-cost benchmark, a 4-axis (compliance,
  price, security, stability) gateway scorecard, dated real-world production
  reviews, and data-backed comparison guides.
